{"tid":2398534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紅磡傳封區　商戶問殯儀車如何處理　交通警：唔知咁多　總之全部走","createTime":"2021-02-07T11:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T15:30:57.000Z","uid":5195,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"5b150328c65b721ad4ba03d8f65f817695b38a23","tid":2398534,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:32:37.000Z","msg":"政府今晚繼續「封區」，有傳紅磡曲街一帶亦在被封之列。晚上 7 時許，《立場》記者在紅磡現場觀察，有交通警員在紅磡曲街巡邏，並記下街上停泊車輛的車牌。<br />\n紅磡一帶有不少殯儀館，街上停泊的殯儀車也逃不過被「抄牌」命運。<br />\n<br />\n有附近商戶上前詢問警員「幾時封區」、「最遲幾時要開走」等問題，交通警員一概回覆指「唔知咁多，總之全部車都要走」。<br />\n<br />\n攝：Sheryl Wong<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KAA7D0u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKAA7D0u.jpg&h=cc636d16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be4d66a995f6dfb52eaad31e4dc6cb7102d8c298","tid":2398534,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65d1165086eb59237c60535c2bf726df243d10b","tid":2398534,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:34:03.000Z","msg":"聽日點出殯"},{"pid":"9e8a07519dd797a2144c1c0c3b1677b4e4897003","tid":2398534,"uid":35930,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be4d66a995f6dfb52eaad31e4dc6cb7102d8c298","tid":2398534,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T11:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><